# Vibe Coder — Dashboard Redesign Walkthrough

## Summary

Redesigned the Open Source Dashboard as **"Vibe Coder"** with a retro pixel-art, terminal-inspired aesthetic inspired by The Sandbox website. All original functionality (profile, repos, trending, issues, roadmap) is preserved with live GitHub data.

## Visual Design

- **Pixel font** (Press Start 2P) for headers, **monospace** (Space Mono / JetBrains Mono) for body text
- **Orange/amber accents** (`#e87400`) on a matte dark background
- **Terminal-window hero** with red/yellow/green traffic light dots
- **CRT scanline overlay** and blue edge glow
- **Sticky top nav bar** with `Vibe Coder /DASHBOARD` branding
- **Announcement bar** for status info

